## AREA 7: Modal Enhancement

### Current State (lines 2739-2772 of JSX, CSS lines 497-540)
The clear doodles confirmation modal uses a plain `<div className="fw-modal-backdrop">` with a static `<div className="fw-modal-card">`.

### JSX Changes

Wrap the entire modal in `AnimatePresence` and replace divs with motion.div:

```jsx
